{"tid":578252,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"愛瑪史東拒演《神奇女俠2》大反派","createTime":"2018-03-02T12:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T02:22:17.000Z","uid":52215,"like":62,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"cce0c110148382e99af9a130fd0db80da34d6d43","tid":578252,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/204507_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F204507_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=728b6cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】姬嘉鐸(Gal Gadot)主演的DC超級英雄片《神奇女俠》(Wonder Woman)去年全球大收逾8億美元票房，更被譽為是DC到目前為止拍得最好的一套超英片。電影成績理想，電影公司決定添食開拍續集。有指電影公司本想邀請奧斯卡影后愛瑪史東(Emma Stone)飾演大反派「豹女」Cheetah，不過已被愛瑪史東拒絕，可能是因為姬嘉鐸暫時仍未夠班與她合作。根據網站HollywoodLife報道，電影公司已搵喜劇節目《Saturday Night Live》的女星Kristen Wiig飾演「豹女」一角。<br />\n<br />\n　　《神奇女俠2》繼續由Patty Jenkins執導，預計明年11月上映，故事背景設定在1980年美蘇冷戰時期，劇情會講述Diana Prince跟Steve Trevor對抗蘇聯軍團，豹女(Cheetah)將會是電影中的重量級反派。"},{"pid":"0cb194e1fb918cd8d8abbada4b6d47eae8a96de6","tid":578252,"uid":23829,"like":8,"dislike":25,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"睇錯英超片"},{"pid":"a917a199a5d9d0b8f996274f32c61f616c74b3d7","tid":578252,"uid":49391,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"唔搵黑人黎演?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a17a1f46f6b0c14a589fa4d0c183c166d5fee6","tid":578252,"uid":86587,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"Steve未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cb7d461b64941f357a155747feeb591384cae3","tid":578252,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a17a1f46f6b0c14a589fa4d0c183c166d5fee6","tid":578252,"uid":86587,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:13.000Z","